sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant TC as TaskController
    participant TS as TaskService
    participant STS as SubTaskService
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant R as Redis
    participant SG as SocketGateway

    Note over U,SG: Create Task
    U->>TC: POST /tasks
    TC->>TS: create(taskDto, userId)
    TS->>DB: insert(task)
    TS->>R: cache task details
    TS-->>TC: created task
    TC-->>U: 201 Created

    Note over U,SG: Get My Tasks
    U->>TC: GET /tasks/my
    TC->>TS: getTasksByUserId(userId)
    TS->>R: check cache
    alt Cache Miss
        TS->>DB: find with filters
        DB-->>TS: tasks
        TS->>R: cache results
    end
    TS-->>TC: tasks
    TC-->>U: 200 OK + tasks

    Note over U,SG: Add Subtask
    U->>TC: POST /tasks/:id/subtasks
    TC->>TS: addSubtask(taskId, title, order, userId)
    TS->>STS: createSubTask(dto, userId)
    STS->>DB: insert(subTask)
    STS->>DB: update task counts
    STS->>SG: emit('subtask-created')
    STS->>R: invalidate task cache
    STS-->>TS: subTask
    TS-->>TC: subTask
    TC-->>U: 201 Created

    Note over U,SG: Toggle Subtask
    U->>TC: PUT /subtasks/:id/toggle
    TC->>STS: toggleSubTaskStatus(id, userId)
    STS->>DB: update subTask.isCompleted
    STS->>DB: recalculate task stats
    STS->>SG: emit('subtask-toggled')
    STS->>R: invalidate cache
    STS-->>TC: updated subTask
    TC-->>U: 200 OK

    Note over U,SG: Get Daily Progress
    U->>TC: GET /tasks/daily-progress?date=2026-03-18
    TC->>TS: getDailyProgress(userId, date)
    TS->>DB: find tasks by date range
    TS->>DB: aggregate subTask stats
    DB-->>TS: progress data
    TS-->>TC: daily progress
    TC-->>U: 200 OK + progress

    Note over U,SG: Get Statistics
    U->>TC: GET /tasks/statistics
    TC->>TS: getTaskStatistics(userId)
    TS->>DB: count by status (parallel)
    DB-->>TS: stats
    TS-->>TC: statistics
    TC-->>U: 200 OK + stats
